WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
When theater output rises but outcomes stay flat, decision rhythm is usually the bottleneck.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Without a clear review habit, gamification quality drifts even when effort increases. Gamification only works when...

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Start with one owner, one metric, and one weekly checkpoint tied to a real decision.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Use a one-week pilot to test behavior change and keep evidence from the workflow.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
This usually improves first-pass quality, cleaner gamification handoffs, and faster team adoption.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Which weekly checkpoint would improve decision quality first?
